---
<section id="experience" class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Work Experience</h2>
        <div class="experience-grid">
            <div class="card experience-card">
                <div class="experience-header">
                    <h3>DevOps Engineer — Site Reliability Engineer</h3>
                    <p class="company">Sahasrara Metatech Pvt. Ltd. · Mumbai, India</p>
                    <p class="duration">Jun 2025 – Present</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="achievements">
                    <li>Architected enterprise CI/CD (Jenkins Groovy, GitLab CI) for 15+ microservices — deployment time 67% (45→15 min), 99.97% success rate</li>
                    <li>Managed production GKE clusters (15+ microservices) with Helm, HPA/VPA, pod disruption budgets — 99.95% SLA, 30% cost reduction</li>
                    <li>Implemented GitOps with ArgoCD for dev/staging/prod — ≤5min cycles with drift detection & self-healing</li>
                    <li>Automated GCP infra (VPC, GKE, Cloud SQL, IAM, Cloud Functions) via Terraform IaC — provisioning from days to hours</li>
                    <li>Integrated observability (SigNoz, Prometheus exporters, Grafana) with distributed tracing — MTTR 67% (2h→40min)</li>
                    <li>Blue-Green/Canary via Istio service mesh — zero-downtime releases, progressive traffic shifting (10%→100%)</li>
                    <li>Security: Trivy scanning, Google Secret Manager, RBAC, network policies, automated patching — SOC2 compliance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card experience-card">
                <div class="experience-header">
                    <h3>DevOps Engineer — Cloud Infrastructure Engineer</h3>
                    <p class="company">StarAgile Pvt. Ltd. · Bengaluru, India</p>
                    <p class="duration">Jan 2025 – May 2025</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="achievements">
                    <li>Built CI/CD pipelines (Jenkins multi-branch, GitHub Actions, Docker, SonarQube, Nexus) — reduced deployment failures 75%</li>
                    <li>Automated AWS infra (VPC, EKS, RDS Multi-AZ, ALB, CloudFront, Route53) via Terraform with S3/DynamoDB state management</li>
                    <li>Deployed microservices on EKS/ECS Fargate with auto-scaling — 10K+ concurrent users, ≤200ms latency</li>
                    <li>Ansible configuration management (playbooks, roles, AWX) for 100+ servers — config errors reduced 85%</li>
                    <li>Monitoring: Prometheus 200+ metrics, Grafana dashboards, ELK Stack 50GB+ daily logs</li>
                    <li>Optimized AWS costs 40% via right-sizing, Reserved/Spot Instances, S3 lifecycle policies</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card experience-card">
                <div class="experience-header">
                    <h3>DevOps Engineer Intern</h3>
                    <p class="company">Cloud Counselage Pvt. Ltd. · Mumbai, India</p>
                    <p class="duration">Feb 2024 – May 2024</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="achievements">
                    <li>Developed Jenkins CI/CD with Docker multi-stage builds, Jenkinsfile pipeline-as-code, webhook triggers — manual ops reduced 85%</li>
                    <li>Integrated security scanning (SonarQube SAST, OWASP ZAP DAST, Snyk) — remediated 200+ vulnerabilities pre-production</li>
                    <li>Collaborated in Agile/Scrum teams for deployment strategies & incident troubleshooting — response time reduced 50%</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--text);
    }

    .experience-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 2rem;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .experience-card {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .experience-header {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .experience-header h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    .company {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin: 0.25rem 0;
    }

    .duration {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text);
        opacity: 0.8;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .achievements {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .achievements li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .achievements li:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .experience-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        }
    }
</style>
